  "comment": "BBP48 Battery Uplight Par 9x 12W IP65: The BBP48 is a compact Battery Par ideal for use as accent and uplighting. The BBP48 is IP65 rated and hence for outdoor and indoor use. It’s equipped with 9x super bright 12W RGBAW-UV LEDs and comes fitted with a fixed built-in battery which will last up to 18 hours when fully charged, depending on colours and intensity. The adjustable foot can be fixed in different angles for angular placement of the par. The BBP48 can communicate in a variety of ways, with DMX and wireless DMX. This makes the units easy to connect to each other.",
